import * as React from "react" import { Paper, Table, TableCell, TableBody, TableHead, TableContainer, TableRow } from "@mui/material" export default function DataDisplay({ mealPrices, total }) { return ( Nombre Coût {mealPrices.map(x => ( {x.label} {x.number} {x.price} € ))} TOTAL {total.number} {total.price} €
) }
